data.description: CASH ONLY. SELLER IS VERY MOTIVATED! Perfect opportunity for first time home buyers or property investors! You must see this duplex in Lehigh Acres: 2,360 total sqft, six bedrooms and four baths. Well maintained duplex to rent both units or live in one and rent the other one to help you with mortgage payments. The #113 unit was totally renovated in Aug 2016. In unit #115, the water system was updated in Aug 2016 and A/C in 2015, that unit went through a total renovation in Jun 2018. This is a great property, in up to date maintenance condition, ready for its new owners. Pictures are of the property before tenants moved in to give the buyer a better comprehension of the layout. Realtors, read confidential remarks.
